idual title\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also won team silver in Rio, before taking broze in both events in Tokyo on Gio.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1745, \"end\": 1748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999021788474, \"rank\": 9.782116563992728e-08, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1788, \"end\": 1793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999974741927029, \"rank\": 2.5258001786980378e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"team silver\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1741}, {\"ngram\": \"broze\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"both events\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1784}, {\"ngram\": \"Gio\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dujardin was due to compete in Paris on new horse Imhotep, both in the individual dressage and the team event alongside Carl Hester and Lottie Fry.\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1834, \"end\": 1839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.213698463742068e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1923, \"end\": 1934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Hester\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carl Hester\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Hester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Hester\"}, {\"begin\": 19