ed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions Make 2026 the year of working smarter \\\"I am deeply ashamed and should have set a better example in that moment.\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2274, \"end\": 2290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Proud\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2188}, {\"ngram\": \"Enhanced Games Sports quiz\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"100 hard questions\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2249}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible year\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2271}, {\"ngram\": \"Grand Slam Track decision\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2322}, {\"ngram\": \"2025 ambitions\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2341}, {\"ngram\": \"a better example\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2437}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am sincerely sorry for my actions and devastated that I have let everyone down, including Team GB, fans and sponsors.\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2552, \"end\": 2559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999940610235997, \"rank\": 5.939007070238648e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my actions\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2495}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2535}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2565}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsors\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will cooperate fully with the FEI, British Equestrian Federation and British Dressage during their investigations, and will not be commenting further until the process is complete.\\\"\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2614, \"end\": 2617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0186192914209311e-35, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2619, \"end\": 2648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Equestrian Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 2653, \"end\": 2669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Dressage\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their investigations\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2697}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"FEI President Ingmar De Vos said: \\\"Charlotte has expressed genuine remorse for her actions, and we recognise and appreciate her willingness to take responsibility.\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2767, \"end\": 2770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0186192914209311e-35, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedi